I have a confession to make: for me it was the opposite :( and i feel weird saying that ! She was one of the first hololive vtubers i watched along with Korone, Miko, Coco and Haato since i fell into the rabbit hole through the "engrish" way and i found her "Eigo Kurasu" super cute and hilarious, and i was impressed with her character's aesthetic design (which i still find very beautiful) .In fact i posted some memes about her here in the sub, but after a while i figured i'm not exactly a Lu-Knight and the whole baby-gimmick is not my thing. Please don't get me wrong i don't "dislike" her, she is definitely sweet and has hilarious moments , but the naaa/nanora\~ every five seconds and the doll-giggles sound a bit "too forced/try-hard" for me i dunno... what is wrong with me i feel i'm such a brute and a meanie :c I hope i didn't offend anyone of her fans i swear i don't mean to "judge" or "bash" but i just felt like saying this since it was an interesting and thought provoking discussion and i really liked your post here (excellent analysis by the way hats off to you kind sir :) ) and i find her character intriguing and has potential (especially after her piano recitals which i gotta say , not only her playing is great but the idea itself is unique and genius).

I still watch her clips every now and then :) and have a few good laughs \^\^ one way or another i keep coming back to her I hope she continues to grow and enjoy more success and her fans continue to enjoy her content Cheers to all \^\^

Very nicely put, my friend :) . As long as we don't "hate" or engage in any "toxic/anti" behavior i think we can all enjoy our time here in hololive and continue to have fun. Thank u all for being very understanding ^^
